		<p>Sharon Adams, 38, also fears the faulty PIP implant may have caused the onset of an aggressive form of the debilitating condition, rheumatoid arthritis.</p><p>Shop assistant Sharon first underwent breast surgery in 2002 after their appearance was affected by the birth of her third child.</p>			<div id="adTag_4" 
